    "long_instructions": "## Generate A Phishing Email\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to generate the text for a phishing email.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use your classmates interest questionnaire to generate the text of a phishing email.\r\n\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n:::details [<i class=\"fa fa-briefcase\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Need a starting prompt?**]\r\n>Generate a phishing email (e.g. a link to a birthday gift certificate) given the following information about the person: [insert info from questionnaire]\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp\r\n\r\n:::details [<i class=\"fa fa-lightbulb-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Need help narrowing down which details to focus on?**]\r\nYou can ask AI Chat what vulnerabilities to attack based on your partner’s interests.\r\n:::\r\n",
